Thu Jun  4 19:55:07 EDT 1998
(Mandrake)
Okay.  Theme loading working its way into the default build.  when main.c is
replaced with test.c now it loads the default definitions file from 
ENLIGHTENMENT_ROOT/definitions (probably should use the config subdir or
something for that...  NOTE TO SELF: should probably change this later)
