into it, which is set to 0 now, so it should try loading a MAIN file out
of your .enlightenment directory next.  Which is what I am shooting for now.
the next step is going to be an actual compile and runtime debugging of
loading this default theme that I am brewing up as I write this.  the
default theme (in theory) should come with my next commit.  Scary stuff,
this is.

