desktop slid underneath others out when in this mode. -also added images for
this.. it all works perfectly.,. added a ListIdemTypeID to list items by
type ANd id (i now use i'ds to class buttons 0 is nromal "user buttons) 1 is
dragbar, 2 is deskray .. etc..all internal use only). I also added images
