really what it's supposed to do, that makes testing a wee bit difficult.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fri Jun 19 01:42:02 EDT 1998
(Mandrake)

these are some notes from over the past few days...
Been working on ImageClass stuff, realized that I didn't allow users
to load disabled images for imageclasses.  fixed that bug.  also
worked on class inheritance for the config loader, and allowing
imageclasses to have their own overlays.

