Sat Jun 27 15:20:09 EDT 1998
(Raster)

Lots of things:
removed crappy (possibly copyrighted) bgs form the pix dir. Fixed 
backgroudns to use one of 3 defined.
fixed desktp bg loader to re-use defined bgs
fixed desktop loader and desktop bg refresher to work 100% properly on multi
depth displays (eg 24+8) - foucn accelX has a bug in 24+8 whereby it "loses"
the framebuffer bits for some windows.. will have to ship this off to xig.
fixed desktop refresher to not accidentally load an extra background when
flipping desktops.
fixed dragbars for bottm and right configs to not accidentaly drag too far
to the bottom and right
fixed resizing of window for sizing to the left or up so it remains
stationary, doesnt jump, and doesnt go sldiin away is i resize too clsoe to
0 in those dirs.
truned of dynamic border chaning caus enetscape does ugly things on tis
transients when they close. not sure exactly why right now, but turning it
off makes things ok again.
added more icons for things like dragbar ordering dragdir chaningng and
others...

