Fri Aug 14 13:28:51 EDT 1998
(Raster)

Fixed doc support - it actually now works - events are captured on "dock
buttons" so you can drag them around - the events are also passed onto the
dock client window, now random apps aren't docked anymore (fixed ICCCM stuff
for that). Bascially it's working now - maybe not pretty.

