-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Tue Sep 22 11:54:36 CDT 1998  mej <mej@mw.3com.com>

	* dox/Makefile.am, eesh/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.am:  Added
	  -I$(prefix)/include to INCLUDES
	* dox/configure.in, eesh/configure.in, src/configure.in:  Removed '-g'
	  from CPPFLAGS.  CPPFLAGS should only consist of flags for 'cpp' to
	  recognize, and '-g' isn't one of those.  '-g' belongs in CFLAGS.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Wed Sep 23 13:36:21 CDT 1998  mej <mej@mw.3com.com>

	* src/tooltips.c: Fixed E seg faulting if the image classes for the
	  hard-coded tooltip were not found.  (Or as raster would say,
	  pffffffft!)

